## ⚙️ How to Run

1. Download or clone the project files  
2. Make sure `index.html`, `style.css`, and `predictor.js` are in the same folder  
3. Open `index.html` in your web browser  
4. Select two teams and click **"Predict Winner"**

## ✏️ Customization

- **Change Background**: Replace `background.jpg` with your own image  
- **Upda**

